data.description: Welcome to this charming and well-maintained home located in beautiful Pueblo West, Colorado. This lovely residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style! A spacious and open floor plan that flows in abundant natural light throughout the home. The kitchen offers a perfect amount of space to prepare home-cooked meals on granite countertops. The primary bedroom has a large walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom that presents a double sink vanity. The main level offers two additional bedrooms and a full bathroom. The fully finished basement offers ample room for an entertainment area. You and your guests will enjoy the wet bar and wiring for an in-home theater system. Already conveniently available with a bedroom and full bathroom, the downstairs offers an opportunity for a fifth bedroom. Enjoy the gorgeous Colorado sunsets and 360-degree views from your back patio. The mud room between the kitchen and garage offers a  free-standing laundry sink. With this property sitting on over an acre, it's zoned for horses and invites the possibility of a large detached garage as well as RV Parking! This home is within walking distance of Pueblo West High School, Sky View Middle School, and playgrounds. Enjoy a quick five-minute drive to Pueblo Reservoir. Come see this beautiful home today!
